                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-130-victim1125 t18320906-130-viclabel735"></join>. The prisoner came to scour the pots on the 3rd of September, in the morning; I said there were not many to do - he staid about a quarter of an hour; I asked if he was done - he said Yes, and came up with his hat and coat in his hand; he put his coat on, and put his hat down - I took up his hat, and found a quart pot in it - I sent for an officer, who found three pint pots on his person; two of the pints, and the quart pot are mine, and the other is a neighbour's; they are all hent.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I have a very heavy family, and was in distress.</p>
